Revenue Canada 
Manitoba-Seizure of Assets of Individual for Non-payment of Taxes 
Hon. David Tkachuk :
Honourable senators, my question for the Leader of the Government in the Senate regards the recently reported Revenue Canada raid seizing the assets of an individual in Winnipeg for non-payment of taxes.  
